OL,3,CPat Finucane inquiry opens as widow
OL,4,Chopes for 'truth and justice'
OL,6,FThe widow of murdered Belfast
OL,7,Fsolicitor Pat Finucane has described
OL,8,Fthe first day of public inquiry into
OL,9,Fhis death as "monumental".
OL,11,FThe 39-year-old was shot dead at his
OL,12,Ffamily home in north Belfast in 1989
OL,13,Fby the Ulster Defence Association in
OL,14,Fan attack found by a series of probes
OL,15,Fto have involved collusion with the
OL,16,Fstate.
OL,18,FThe Finucane family has been
OL,19,Fcampaigning for decades for a public
OL,20,Finquiry to establish the extent of
OL,21,Fsecurity force involvement.
OL,26,@qD@NOUqD@YO]
