OL,3,CPat Finucane inquiry opens as widow
OL,4,Chopes for 'truth and justice'
OL,6,FGeraldine Finucane arrived in a large
OL,7,Fcoach accompanied by family to
OL,8,FBradford Court in south Belfast for
OL,9,Fthe Patrick Finucane Inquiry on
OL,10,FWednesday.
OL,12,FMrs Finucane said no-one wanted to
OL,13,Fmiss the long-awaited day, as she was
OL,14,Fflanked by her sons Michael and John,
OL,15,Fand daughter Katherine, as well as Mr
OL,16,FFinucane's brothers Martin and Dermot.
OL,18,FShe said: "As you can see by the
OL,19,Fnumber of people who are with me
OL,20,Ftoday, this is a monumental day for
OL,21,Four family.
OL,26,@zD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1781190689
OL,3,CPat Finucane inquiry opens as widow
OL,4,Chopes for 'truth and justice'
OL,6,F"We have waited 37-and-a-half years
OL,7,Ffor this day and not one of us wanted
OL,8,Fto miss it.
OL,10,F"We fought long and hard to get to the
OL,11,Ftruth, and to get to justice, and
OL,12,Fthat's what we're hoping that this
OL,13,Finquiry will provide us with.
OL,15,F"We're hoping that all those questions
OL,16,Fthat have never been fully answered
OL,17,Fwill be answered during the inquiry
OL,18,Fand it will be thorough, and it will
OL,19,Fsatisfy us, and then we will have
OL,20,Fclosure."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
