CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1781190689
OL,3,CPat Finucane inquiry opens as widow
OL,4,Chopes for 'truth and justice'
OL,6,FMrs Finucane described mixed feelings
OL,7,Fon the first hearing day, but
OL,8,Femphasised she was really glad it was
OL,9,Fhappening after previously fearing it
OL,10,Fnever would.
OL,12,F"I'm hoping for the best as usual,
OL,13,Fhoping for no more delays, no more
OL,14,Fobstructions and just so we can get it
OL,15,Ffinished with, and get closure," she
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1781190689
OL,3,CPat Finucane inquiry opens as widow
OL,4,Chopes for 'truth and justice'
OL,6,F"It's more about who was pulling the
OL,7,Fstrings, why was Pat targeted, why
OL,8,Fwere we never warned that he was
OL,9,Ftargeted on more than one occasion,
OL,10,Fwho thought it up, why was this
OL,11,Fstrategy put in place.
OL,13,F"These are questions that need to be
OL,14,Ffully answered, not glided over
OL,15,Fsuperficially anymore.
OL,17,F"This is the opportunity to do that
OL,18,Fand get it right."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOUzD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
