CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1781190689
OL,3,CPat Finucane inquiry opens as widow
OL,4,Chopes for 'truth and justice'
OL,6,FMrs Finucane added: "Maybe we will
OL,7,Ffind out that what happened to Pat
OL,8,Fhappened to a lot of other people, and
OL,9,Fmaybe we will find out the strategy
OL,10,Fbehind it all and who was responsible."
OL,12,FThe inquiry into the circumstances of
OL,13,FMr Finucane's death was announced by
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland Secretary Hilary Benn
OL,15,Fin 2024.
OL,17,FLast June, the Government announced
OL,18,Fsenior judge Sir Gary Hickinbottom as
OL,19,Fchairman of the inquiry.
OL,26,@nD@UOUrD@gO]
